{"tid":409533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉航拍Formula E被控　3男未成功申法援　保釋11月再訊","createTime":"2017-09-22T06:41:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T09:17:26.000Z","uid":389,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8172566b14acc33b4c8b446e7c0cc0ef8f4482f4","tid":409533,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"去年10月，中環舉行Formula E電動方程式錦標賽期間，有3名男子疑因在賽道上空操作航拍機被捕，事後被控3項導致飛機對人或財產造成危害罪，案件今於東區裁判法院提堂。3人暫毋須答辯，案件押至11月17日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/22/144051_a89c5c9ff1e4990b2c7e5d37373c7a38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F22%2F144051_a89c5c9ff1e4990b2c7e5d37373c7a38.jpg&h=0262934b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首被告聶拜一（41歲）報稱為攝影師，次被告容嘉暉（29歲）則報稱無業，二人分別被控於2016年10月9日，在中環龍和道近分域碼頭的中國建築國際集團有限公司地盤內的貨櫃上，魯莽或疏忽地導致飛機對人或財產造成危害。<br />\n<br />\n報稱為電腦工程師的第3被告沈志青（43歲）則被控同日，在中環龍和道南邊行人路近立法會道，魯莽或疏忽地導致飛機對人或財產造成危害。 <br />\n<br />\n3人沒有律師代表，並稱暫時未能成功申請法援。裁判官逐將案件押後，以待各被告索取文件及法律意見，其間各人獲准以500元保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170922/s00001/1506060232846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170922%2Fs00001%2F1506060232846&d=%2B5%2FyjJ4Eu%2Fq2kyZLlrbNTwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=cfeab92d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170922%2Fs00001%2F1506060232846&h=d679ceae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170922/s00001/1506060232846</a>"},{"pid":"3171faac2482af50173b64f439318ca08e44bf8e","tid":409533,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"導致飛機對人或財產造成危害罪 ..<br />\n<br />\n造成 .. 做左?"},{"pid":"35b7d02293f060f6b15384126284cb64b4e2107f","tid":409533,"uid":97080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"reply